value.0: Also known as gray dwarves, the duergar are from the Underdark and are the evil cousins of the surface dwarves.

This heavy iron and stone gate stands firm against all but the most determined assaults.  Crafted with the expert skill of the svirfnebli, it guards the town of Mak'a'nor against incursions from the evil races of the underdark.
A heavy javelin sits in its groove, notched against the ballista's taut-drawn wire. You can imagine how a well-aimed shot might have the power to fell a dragon from the sky.
